Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.34,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手を伸ばして　焦がれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.42,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}届くはずない　光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:54.38,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こんな世界で　こんな世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.97,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}何度も見てた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.56,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}君の割れた　硝子細工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.36,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}触れた指が　痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:16.53,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大切なもの　要らないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.35,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}元には戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.21,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　一雫　頬を濡らして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.13,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}切なく　雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:32.54,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}まだ何も君を知らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.59,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その涙が　止まったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:40.39,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}笑ってみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:44.73,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あ憧れて　憧れて　想像を形へと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:48.64,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}変えるリアリティ　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.98,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行くよ　窓の外は君を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.78,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.40,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.92,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:08.54,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.67,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
Comment: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:43.30,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.34,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我所伸出的手　如此急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.42,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那所无法传达　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:54.38,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地里　在这样的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.97,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若梦　回眸几何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.56,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你所制作的　玻璃饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.36,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}指尖一触　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:16.53,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.35,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至终　覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.21,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}爱　仅需一滴　脸颊便能浸润
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.13,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀绞　雨恨云愁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:32.54,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还是对你　一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.59,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落泪　就此止泣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:40.39,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想与你　欢声笑语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:44.73,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此向往　想象便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:48.64,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改变当下　于晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.98,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出发吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.78,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}携手与你共赏春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.40,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑云已散　风光日霁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.92,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨后镜花水月　依旧彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:08.54,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨过天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.67,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不过我想让你　所寻自己而已
